# STEP 1 — BASIC CONFIGURATION

## SW1

```cisco id="4zjlwm"
enable
configure terminal

hostname SW1
no ip domain-lookup

spanning-tree mode rapid-pvst

vlan 10
 name USERS

interface range g0/1 - 2
 switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
 switchport mode trunk

end
write memory
```

